      *! version 1.0.5  10may2013
program meologit, eclass byable(onecall) prop(or mi)
	
	version 13
	
	if _by() {
		local by "by `_byvars'`_byrc0':"
	}
	if replay() {
		if "`e(cmd)'" != "meologit" {
			error 301
		}
		if _by() {
			error 190
		}
		_me_display `0'
		exit
	}
	
	capture noisily `by' Estimate `0'
	local rc = _rc
	exit `rc'
end

program Estimate, sortpreserve eclass byable(recall)
	
	if _by() {
		tempname bytouse
		mark `bytouse'
	}
	
	local 0_orig `0'
	_parse expand eq opt : 0
	local gopts `opt_op'
	
	forvalues i=1/`=`eq_n'-1' {
		local 0 `eq_`i''
		syntax [anything] [if] [in] [, irr BINomial(string) 	///
			Family(string) Link(string) EXPosure(string) *]
		_me_chk_opts, binomial(`binomial') exposure(`exposure')  ///
			irr(`irr') family(`family') link(`link')
		local eqs `eqs' `eq_`i'' ||
	}
	
	local 0 `eq_`eq_n''
	syntax [anything] [if] [in] [, *]
	local eqn `anything' `if' `in'
	local 0 , `options' `gopts'
	syntax [anything] [, noRETable noFETable noTABle noLRtest noGRoup ///
		noHEADer noLOg or irr eform Family(string) Link(string)	  ///
		EXPosure(string) * ]
	
	_me_chk_opts, family(`family') link(`link') exposure(`exposure') ///
		irr(`irr') binomial(`binomial')
	
	_get_diopts diopts opts, `options'
	local diopts `diopts' `table' `lrtest' `group' `header' `log' 	///
		`or' `eform'
	
	local 0 `eqs' `eqn' , link(logit) fam(ordinal) `opts' `log'
	`by' _me_estimate "`bytouse'" `0'
	
	ereturn local family ordinal
	ereturn local link logit
	
	if e(k_r) ereturn local title "Mixed-effects ologit regression"
	else ereturn local title "Ordered logistic regression"
	ereturn local model ologit
	
	ereturn local cmd meologit
	ereturn local cmdline meologit `0_orig'

	ereturn local predict meologit_p
	ereturn hidden local cmd2 meglm
	ereturn local cmdline2
	
	_me_display , `diopts'
	
end
exit
